name: Queer NFT; Series 4-NFT Holes; No. 4
description: @queernft - An established artist claiming an NFT space for queer expression. The commercial world of art has held our community back, prevented us from showing work that reflects 100% of who we are. So I am here now, sharing my hidden works with the world as NFT. Series 4, NFT Holes, my first set of paintings created solely as an NFT project, exploring the last frontier of the male body, the anus.
